<TEXT>
The US-EC farm trade deal has widened divisions within the Dutch farm
sector, industry officials said yesterday, Reuter reports in Amsterdam.
Farmers in the Netherlands - the world's third largest agricultural exporter
after the US and France - are struggling in vain to find a common stand on
