              PROJECTED AVERAGE COUNCIL TAX BILLS
 --------------------------------------------------------------
Band                   Property value           Bill
 --------------------------------------------------------------
A                 up to Pounds 40,000     Pounds 329
B        Pounds 40,000- Pounds 52,000     Pounds 384
C        Pounds 52,000- Pounds 68,000     Pounds 439
D        Pounds 68,000- Pounds 88,000     Pounds 494
E       Pounds 88,000- Pounds 120,000     Pounds 604
F      Pounds 120,000- Pounds 160,000     Pounds 713
G      Pounds 160,000- Pounds 320,000     Pounds 823
H                 over Pounds 320,000     Pounds 988
 --------------------------------------------------------------
Calculations based on government estimate of Pounds 439 for band C if
councils spend in line with its assumptions. Figures do not take
account of local variations - for example, the extra amounts
councils may levy to make up for poll tax arrears.
