Sumitomo              37.8           -40.7         8.82         8.43
Mitsubishi            32.6           -37.6         8.73         8.20
Sakura                28.0           -40.8         9.37         7.92
Fuji                  26.0           -56.6         8.71         8.04
DKB                   29.0           -42.4         8.53         8.25
Tokyo                 23.5           -18.0         8.30         8.12
